news.title: Nagpur: Set up EV charging station on premises, get 2% property tax rebate
news.para: According to the order, individuals will get a 2% rebate in property tax if they set up charging stations for their own vehicles and make the facility available to owners of other electric vehicles.

news.title: Nashik civic body to make names of property tax defaulters public
news.para: NMC’s property tax department officials said the names of defaulters will be uploaded on its website. This is likely to have an impact on the defaulters as others would come to know that they are defaulters, said the officials.

news.title: Indore civic body to collect over 1.5 times property tax from defaulters
news.para: ​​​“The new amendment allows the Municipal Corporation to collect 1.5 to 2 times of the property tax from residential property owners in case of a delay,” IMC’s additional commissioner Bhavya Mittal said.
